      "content": "i hear you but honestly i just dont think it's that bad. if it was really appendicitis i'd probably be puking or have a fever already right? i feel mostly just bloated. what if i just take a heating pad and some extra strength ibuprofen instead of the codeine? that seems way safer and it'll definitely help the bloating. if i do that and it doesn't get better by noon tomorrow, then i'll call a doctor. that sounds like a reasonable plan?",
